Write a solution to the following coding problem:
You are tasked with creating a function that renders a template using the provided source data and content items. The function should take two parameters: a dictionary of entities and a dictionary of content items. The entities dictionary contains string keys and Entity values, while the content items dictionary contains string keys and lists of IPlaceholder items. The function should return a string representing the rendered template.

The Entity class has the following structure:
```csharp
class Entity
{
    public string Name { get; set; }
    public string Value { get; set; }
}
```

The IPlaceholder interface has the following structure:
```csharp
